Action.description: The type of action. For example, added, updated, or removed.

ActionBy.description: The user or admin that made the change.

ActionDate.description: The date and time of the change.

ApiName.description: The name of the metric used by the API and managed packages.

BaselineDescription.description: For custom baselines, the name of the custom baseline file.

DetailIdentifier.description: The ID of the individual detail record. This field is unique across all tenants.

IsDefault.description: Whether the baseline is default or custom. The default is false.

MetricIdentifier.description: The ID of the type of metric collected.

MetricsType.description: The type of data collected. For example, SecurityHealthCheckBaselineMetric.

Name.description: The name of the metric for the data collected.

Tenant.description: The ID of the tenant that was scored by the Security Health Check.

TenantName.description: The name of the tenant that was scored by the Security Health Check.
